e":"2018-04-05T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/204009_681ac007707b8232b73d511cab0d4760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F204009_681ac007707b8232b73d511cab0d4760.jpg&h=6c79deb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東歐都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"我讀嗰間有水池仲有埋尊孔子像，正宗掛羊頭賣狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a9eeb14a0395d44350e14ed5f15e1bbf8e4616","tid":617913,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"係咪Usyd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早幾年達賴喇嘛黎開talk<br />\n有傳因為孔子學院既原因搞到大學取消左個talk<br />\n<br />\n跟住澳洲政府+ d MP向大學施壓，最後又搞得返成, 雖然個talk最後變左off campus"},{"pid":"ca55dce345a104bd8b738b139b2d27dafb7a7783","tid":617913,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"洗腦基地，間諜地方，<br />\n唔好喺嗰到講反中國言論，<br />\n佢哋有人mon住㗎，<br />\n比佢哋知道你反中國，台獨等等，<br />\n你一定被坐洗頭艇返大陸，之後被自殺的。"},{"pid":"51e41531371fc094b7889719b29a3fcd58197ddb","tid":617913,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"中華民國萬歲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎各位去隔離我個post嗰度細心睇曬全文，希望大家可以為香港開創一個新前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「港獨，回歸中華民國係香港唯二出路」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/616967/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/616967/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"0dafc2a3ebf78cfd0cc3be858ef37b29cf8ceffd","tid":617913,"uid":174342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43a9eeb14a0395d44350e14ed5f15e1bbf8e4616","tid":617913,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"係咪Usyd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c